author: Zoe Shenton
title: Kylie Jenner debuts bright orange hair as she's mobbed by fans at launch of New York pop up shop
text:
Kylie Jenner debuts bright orange hair as she's mobbed by fans at launch of New York pop up shop The teen entrepreneur opened her second shop in the Big Apple on Monday   Kylie Jenner debuts ORANGE HAIR at pop-up store launch   celebs   
Kylie Jenner debuted a brand new bright orange hue as she opened her second pop up store on Monday. 
The 19-year-old star's highly-anticipated temporary store for her beauty empire Kylie Cosmetics was launched on Mercer street in New York. 
Dressed in an eye-catching thigh-skimming tan dress and fur jacket which she wore draped over her shoulders, Kylie was mobbed by fans as she officially opened the shop. 
And with the less-than-casual get up and her new bold wig, the star made sure she was the centre of attention for the occasion. Kylie Jenner, Tyga (Photo: Rex Features) Kylie Jenner's pop-up store (Photo: Instagram) Read More Kylie Jenner shamelessly flashes her nude knickers and bra in see-through bodysuit on New York dinner date 
The Keeping Up With The Kardashians beauty was joined by her beau Tyga, who later took to Instagram to congratulate her on the launch. 
Alongside a picture of the loved-up pair cuddling up to one another inside the shop, the 27-year-old Rack City rapper wrote: "Congratulations on your NYC Pop up Store!!!" 
Last week, the teen teased fans with details of the opening when she shared an image of the outside of the building with boards emblazoned with pink dripping liquid covering the windows to her Instagram account. Kylie Jenner, Tyga (Photo: Rex Features) Kylie Jenner, Tyga (Photo: Rex Features) 
She captioned the post: "Wow can't believe I'm coming to NYC next week to open up my second Pop Up Shop.. DREAMS!!! I'll see you guys there. 
"Address: 27 Mercer St. New York City 
"When: 2/13/17 I'll open the doors at 10am that morning & will be open daily until 9pm! (sic)." 
Kylie also promised her store will stay open for Valentine's Day on February 14, unless all of her stock has sold out. Kylie Jenner (Photo: Splash News) Kylie Jenner, Tyga (Photo: Splash News) 
She continued: "Store will stay there until supplies run out! XOXO 
"** Yes, we will be open on Valentines Day (sic)." 
The make-up brand has also shared the picture on their photo-sharing site, with the caption: "WE CANT WAIT!!!! who's going to be there?! (sic)." 
And the brunette star has also teased a new collection for Kendall + Kylie is "coming soon". 
The entrepreneur and Kendall, 21, launched their first collection under the eponymous label in 2015 with Topshop, and the pair have revealed they have been working on another line Drop One on social media. 
Kylie shared a string of images on her Instagram account of her from the campaign. https://www.instagram.com/p/BQeSJGVAyyQ/?taken-by=kinggoldchains&hl=en/embed Kylie Jenner (Photo: Splash News) 
Alongside a picture of the star wearing a black bustier and grey ruched trousers, whilst her raven-haired tresses are styled in a sleek straight crop, she wrote: "DropOne @kendallandkylie Coming Soon (sic)." 
And Kendall has also shared an image from the campaign of her laying back on a chair whilst wearing a white ribbed top, jeans and clear perspex heeled shoes. 
She also captioned the post: "DropOne @kendallandkylie coming soon (sic)." 
However, the pair have yet to divulge any further details about the upcoming capsule, including when it will be available to buy. Like us on Facebook
